      <h2 id="special-messages-of-comfort-and-hope">Special Messages of Comfort and Hope</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>In closing, these messages offer a glimmer of hope and peace amid grief.</p>
<p>May the beautiful memories you shared with your loved one bring you peace and comfort in the coming days.  May time heal your sorrow, and may you find strength in the love surrounding you.  Remember that grief is a natural process, and allow yourself the time and space you need to heal.  Know that you are not alone, and that support is available when you need it most.  Peace be with you.</p>
    
  
